Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Prowler Installation Fails
Solution: Ensure Python 3.8+ is installed and pip is updated:

python3 --version
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install prowler --no-cache-dir
Issue: AWS Credentials Not Found
Solution: Verify credentials file exists and has correct format:

cat ~/.aws/credentials
aws configure list
Issue: Scan Produces No Results
Solution: Check that:

AWS credentials are valid (in production environment)
Proper IAM permissions are configured
Network connectivity to AWS services is available
Prowler command syntax is correct
Issue: Python Script Execution Errors
Solution: Verify:

Virtual environment is activated
All required packages are installed: pip list
Script has execute permissions: chmod +x script.py
Python path is correct: which python3
